#

Crispy Skin Salmon with Lemon Herb Butter

$25
500 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

FishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

SeafoodDinnerHealthyQuick

Description

A perfectly seared salmon fillet with a crispy skin, topped with a zesty lemon herb butter that elevates the dish.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillet: 2 pieces (6 oz each)
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Fresh parsley, chopped: 2 tbsp
  • Fresh dill, chopped: 1 tbsp
  • Lemon juice: 1 tbsp
  • Garlic, minced: 1 clove
